text: - [Announcer] Find, subscribe to

and use third-party healthcare
(soft music)

and life sciences, data
sets as files, databases
or APIs with AWS Data Exchange.
Discover and evaluate data sets

that can help you
quantify health outcomes,
accelerate research and clinical trials,
create novel therapies

and understand patient sentiment
with AWS Data Exchange.
Once you are subscribed

to data products from
chosen data providers,

you can access the data in
just a few clicks directly
in your AWS analytics environments

and combine this data with
your internal data sets.

AWS Data Exchange is a
fully managed, secure

and compliant service that
will deliver the data sets
to you from data providers,

reducing your IT operation
burden and accelerating time
to insights generated.

Numerous data providers
offer flexible trials

so you can evaluate the
data before you subscribe.
You will also find hundreds

of free public data sources
to support your analysis.
Learn more and get started today.
(soft music)
